OL,3,CNew plan in the making for Jersey's
OL,4,CFort Regent
OL,6,FInfrastructure Minister is working on
OL,7,Fnew plans to refurbish Fort Regent in
OL,8,FSt Helier.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News, Constable Andy
OL,11,FJehan said: "I'd like to see Fort
OL,12,FRegent refurbished and reopened as
OL,13,Fquickly as we possibly can.
OL,15,F"That's going to take a lot of effort
OL,16,Fand we need to make sure that whatever
OL,17,Fwe do there is sustainable, and we
OL,18,Fneed to make sure that we generate
OL,19,Fsufficient revenue to maintain the
OL,20,Fproperty moving forward.
