OL,6,FWhen asked how much the Government
OL,7,Fwould have to rely on the private
OL,8,Fsector, Constable Jehan said: "That
OL,9,Fdepends on the model we use. Revenue
OL,10,Fis really important - we want to
OL,11,Fprovide facilities for young and old
OL,12,Falike, so people have got somewhere to
OL,13,Fgo indoors and do sporting activities,
OL,14,Fleisure activities and I think the
OL,15,Flatest plans are far more reasonable
OL,16,Fthan the plans of a couple of years
OL,17,Fago and are achievable.
OL,19,F"Clearly, the Fort is not looking as
OL,20,Fgood as it should do and we need to
OL,21,Fcrack on and make some decisions."
