OL,4,CFort Regent
OL,6,FFort Regent has been subject to at
OL,7,Fleast three plans in the last decade,
OL,8,Fall of which have been abandoned by
OL,9,Fprevious politicians.
OL,11,FSandra Monacella remembers Fort Regent
OL,12,Fin its heyday and said: "It was such a
OL,13,Fpopular venue for everybody. Where do
OL,14,Fwe go for a proper concert nowadays?
OL,15,FThe Government wastes so much money on
OL,16,Fsilly little things."
